- FileSink should be able to specify overwrite/not overwrite.
- FileSink should be able to append to an existing file.
- Deal with asynchronous file access.
  > Assumes success, unless something throws
  > Correctly journals on failure
  > If journaling is not enabled, fails rather hard on failure
  > Should be a type of FileSink
- Journal should have a standardised way to write/read to/from file
- ...
